I thought plastic beach was bad... I think this is actually worse. No_limit1, you got my hopes up for nothing. lol At least I kinda liked the last song in plastic beach (pirate jet). This one... no. There's not one song I like, or even tolerate listening to. At all. Gorillaz... I am disappointed.
The slow growers are the best though krazcain. Give Plastic beach a few more listens. I fuckin love it now.

Everyone says Plastic Beach sucked but most people never really listened to it, it's a decent album there's lots of songs people never gave a chance.
haven't heard much from this one but i'm starting to love Plastic Beach, a bit wierd at first but it grew on me... STYLO MO'FUCKAS!!!!
Plastic Beach is a masterpiece, i thought it was their best album to date.
Plastic Beach is epic. A true artwork.

While Plastic Beach might not have been as good and certainly didn't have the same charm as previous Gorillaz albums, 
it was still a well-made album and nice to listen to.

I hope this album is about as good/better.
